### Time Event API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Get Server Time
GET {{baseUrl}}/time-events/server-time

### 2. Get Employee Status (Initially CLOCKED_OUT)
# Assuming employee 2025001 exists from previous setup
GET {{baseUrl}}/time-events/status/2025001

### 3. Clock In (Success)
# Replace requestId with a unique UUID for each run
POST {{baseUrl}}/time-events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeNumber": "2025001",
  "type": "CLOCK_IN",
  "requestId": "{{$guid}}",
  "source": "KIOSK"
}

### 4. Get Employee Status (Should be CLOCKED_IN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/time-events/status/2025001

### 5. Break In
POST {{baseUrl}}/time-events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeNumber": "2025001",
  "type": "BREAK_IN",
  "requestId": "{{$guid}}"
}

